                          ===========================
                          Advance Binary Installation
                          ===========================

As root or user type:

    ./configure

and as root type:

    make install

The binaries are installed in $prefix/bin, the documentation
in $prefix/share/advance/doc, the program data in $prefix/share/advance and
the man pages in $prefix/man/man1

The default installation $prefix is /usr/local

